params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"SHIP_INVOICE_NO\\" AS \\"SHIP_INVOICE_NO\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"DEPARTURE_PLACE\\" AS \\"DEPARTURE_PLACE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"DEPARTURE_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS \\"DEPARTURE_DATE\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"ARRIVAL_PLACE\\" AS \\"ARRIVAL_PLACE\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"ARRIVAL_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS \\"ARRIVAL_DATE\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"TRANSPORT_METHOD\\" AS \\"TRANSPORT_METHOD\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"SHIP_NO\\" AS \\"SHIP_NO\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"REMARKS_1\\" AS \\"REMARKS_1\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"REMARKS_2\\" AS \\"REMARKS_2\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"CUST_CD\\" AS \\"CUST_CD\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"DLV_LOC_CD\\" AS \\"DLV_LOC_CD\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"INVOICE_AMOUNT\\" AS \\"INVOICE_AMOUNT\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"INVOICE_TAX_AMOUNT\\" AS \\"INVOICE_TAX_AMOUNT\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"PRINT_FLG\\" AS \\"PRINT_FLG\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"SHIP_PLAN_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') AS \\"SHIP_PLAN_DATE\\", " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" AS \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" " +"FROM " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD " +"WHERE " +" SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = ?"

"SELECT " +" a.\\"SLIP_DETAIL_NO\\" AS \\"SLIP_DETAIL_NO\\", " +" a.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\", " +" a.\\"CUST_ODR_NO\\" AS \\"CUST_ODR_NO\\", " +" a.\\"ODR_NO\\" AS \\"ODR_NO\\", " +" a.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" a.\\"SHIP_ODR_NO\\" AS \\"SHIP_ODR_NO\\", " +" a.\\"SHIP_QTY\\" AS \\"SHIP_QTY\\", " +" a.\\"UNIT_PRICE\\" AS \\"UNIT_PRICE\\", " +" a.\\"SHIP_ODR_AMOUNT\\" AS \\"SHIP_ODR_AMOUNT\\", " +" a.\\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\" AS \\"UNIT_COST_TYP\\", " +" a.\\"TAX_AMOUNT\\" AS \\"TAX_AMOUNT\\", " +" a.\\"TAX_RATE\\" AS \\"TAX_RATE\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_NAME, " +" c.PART_DLV_SEQ_NO, " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_NAME " +"FROM " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_DETAIL a, " +" M_ITEM, " +" T_SHIP_ODR c, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC " +"WHERE " +" a.SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = ? " +" and a.SHIP_ODR_NO = c.SHIP_ODR_NO " +" and M_ITEM_SPEC.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" and c.CUST_CD = M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_CD " +" and a.CUST_ITEM_CD = M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_CD " +" and c.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +"ORDER BY c.ODR_NO"

"SELECT " +" c.\\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"CUST_ITEM_CD\\", " +" c.\\"CUST_ODR_NO\\" AS \\"CUST_ODR_NO\\", " +" c.\\"ODR_NO\\" AS \\"ODR_NO\\", " +" c.\\"ITEM_CD\\" AS \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" c.\\"SHIP_QTY\\" AS \\"SHIP_QTY\\", " +" c.\\"UNIT_PRICE\\" AS \\"UNIT_PRICE\\", " +" c.\\"SHIP_ODR_AMOUNT\\" AS \\"SHIP_ODR_AMOUNT\\", " +" M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_NAME, " +" c.PART_DLV_SEQ_NO, " +" M_ITEM.ITEM_NAME, " +" c.\\"CUST_CD\\" AS \\"CUST_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(c.\\"DESINATED_SHIP_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"DESINATED_SHIP_DATE\\", " +" c.\\"DLV_LOC_CD\\" AS \\"DLV_LOC_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(c.\\"SCDL_DLV_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"SCDL_DLV_DATE\\" " +"FROM " +" M_ITEM, " +" T_SHIP_ODR c, " +" M_ITEM_SPEC, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY " +"WHERE " +" c.SHIP_ODR_NO = ? " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.COMPANY_CD = M_ITEM_SPEC.COMPANY_CD " +" and c.CUST_CD = M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_CD " +" and c.CUST_ITEM_CD = M_ITEM_SPEC.CUST_ITEM_CD " +" and SYS_MY_COMPANY.CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +" and c.ITEM_CD = M_ITEM.ITEM_CD " +"ORDER BY " +" c.ODR_NO"

"SELECT " +" a.UNIT_COST_TYP " +"FROM " +" M_UNIT_COST a, " +" T_SHIP_ODR b, " +" SYS_MY_COMPANY c " +"WHERE " +" a.EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE <= SYSDATE " +" AND a.COMPANY_CD = c.COMPANY_CD " +" AND a.CUST_CD = b.CUST_CD " +" AND a.ITEM_CD = ? " +" AND b.SHIP_ODR_NO = ? " +" AND c.CTRL_CD = 'SYSTEM' " +"ORDER BY " +" a.EFF_PHASE_IN_DATE DESC"

"select " +" substr(M_TAX.\\"TAX_CD\\", 3, 1) as \\"TAX_KBN\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"OLD_TAX_RATE_1\\" as \\"OLD_TAX_1\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"OLD_TAX_RATE_2\\" as \\"OLD_TAX_2\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"OLD_TAX_RATE_3\\" as \\"OLD_TAX_3\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"NEW_TAX_RATE_1\\" as \\"NEW_TAX_1\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"NEW_TAX_RATE_2\\" as \\"NEW_TAX_2\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"NEW_TAX_RATE_3\\" as \\"NEW_TAX_3\\", " +" TO_CHAR(M_TAX.\\"NEW_TAX_RATE_START_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD') as \\"START_DATE\\", " +" M_TAX.\\"ROUND_TYP\\" as \\"ROUND_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_TAX " +"where " +" TAX_CD IN ( " +" SELECT " +" TAX_CD " +" FROM " +" T_ODR " +" WHERE " +" ODR_NO = ? " +" )"
"SELECT " +" M_CUR.\\"DECIMAL_FIG\\" " +"FROM " +" M_CUR, " +" M_CUST " +"WHERE " +" M_CUR.\\"CUR_CD\\" = M_CUST.\\"CUR_CD\\" " +" AND M_CUST.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ? " +" AND CUST_CD = ?"

"select " +" INVOICE_AMOUNT, " +" INVOICE_TAX_AMOUNT, " +" TAX_INCLUDE_AMOUNT, " +" TAX_CREDIT_AMOUNT, " +" CUST_CD, " +" SHIP_PLAN_DATE, " +" INVOICE_AMOUNT, " +" INVOICE_TAX_AMOUNT " +"from " +" M_SHIP_INVOICE_HEAD " +"where " +" SHIP_INVOICE_CTL_NO = ?"
